data.description: Move-in ready charmer on quiet cul-de-sac! Well-maintained 1,961 square foot, 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom split-level offers comfortable living & space for entertaining. The circular driveway offers convenient parking for guests or multiple vehicles. New roof. Spacious yard w/2 sheds to provide ample storage. Laminate flooring flows throughout, creating a cohesive look. Sliding doors off dining room lead to large back deck, perfect for indoor-outdoor entertaining. Cozy propane fireplace heats entire home efficiently, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. Bonus lower level features a propane stove for alternative heating options & additional living space. Amenity-filled, gated community w/swimming pools, lakes, fitness center & playgrounds. Convenient to major highways & attractions. Comes with a Home Warranty transferrable to the buyers upon closing.
